{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/how-to-change-the-header-logo-on-your-shopify-theme","result":{"pageContext":{"id":569,"date":"2021-03-18T18:25:51","date_gmt":"2021-03-18T18:25:51","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=569"},"modified":"2021-03-18T18:30:05","modified_gmt":"2021-03-18T18:30:05","slug":"how-to-change-the-header-logo-on-your-shopify-theme","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/how-to-change-the-header-logo-on-your-shopify-theme/","title":{"rendered":"How to change the header logo on your Shopify theme"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Most (if not all) free and premium themes come with a built-in option to change your header&#8217;s logo via the Customize page. This is how you can do it:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Finding the customize page</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>> <strong>Customize</strong>.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1699\" height=\"751\" class=\"wp-image-570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg 1699w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-600x265.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1200x530.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-768x339.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1536x679.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" /></li><li>On the left sidebar, click on <strong>header</strong>. Typically this is the very first option.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1392\" height=\"647\" class=\"wp-image-572\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/header123.jpg\" alt=\"header\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/header123.jpg 1392w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/header123-600x279.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/header123-1200x558.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/header123-768x357.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px\" /></li><li>Search for an option called <strong>Logo Image</strong>. This name may vary from theme to theme, so does its position. Make sure you scroll through all the options to ensure you locate the correct one. <br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"678\" height=\"724\" class=\"wp-image-576\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/logo123.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/logo123.jpg 678w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/logo123-600x641.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 678px) 100vw, 678px\" /></li><li>Click on <strong>select image</strong> to choose your the logo you wish.</li><li>Click on <strong>save </strong>at the top right corner and that is it! You can now preview your website to ensure it&#8217;s showing up correctly.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Change or update your theme&#8217;s logo. Works with any Shopify theme.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":584,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[206,154],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-8-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-8-100x100.png","post_count":1,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["all themes","Code Tutorial"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/569"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=569"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/569/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":591,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/569/revisions/591"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/584"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=569"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=569"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=569"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1739988571","1995349551"]}